Unripe plantains are nutritious, although sweet tooths find it unpleasant unless they are made into chips. But there are various ways to make this food palatable and a must-have. Puerto Rican Tostones are unripe fried plantains that are prepared in a different way than chips. It takes care and patience to prepare and is really tasty and can be nibbled alone or combined with other food. Puerto Rican Tostones. Photo: YouTube